data.description: This beautiful hill country lot in the desirable Canyon Lake community of Scenic Heights is a must see. This lot is conveniently located near the Guadalupe River, Canyon Lake, tubing & White Water Amphitheater. Close to everything; yet away from it all! Bring your ideas and build your dream retreat! Many opportunities to choose from, investors welcome!
